
in terminal

1- roslaunch my_robot_description spawn.launch

2- rosrun my_robot_description main.py 

3- roslaunch my_odom_publisher start_odom.launch


4-rostopic echo /my_odom/pose/pose/orientation/z
 or 
 
 rostopic echo /my_odom/pose/pose/position/x
 
 
 
